Package: MRSea
Title: Marine Renewables Strategic environmental assessment
Description: Examines animal survey data for signs of changes in animal
    abundance and distribution following marine renewables development. The
    functions of this package can be used to analyse segmented line transect data
    and nearshore vantage point data. The package includes functions for fitting
    spatially adaptive one and 2D smoothers using SALSA and CReSS. Non-parametric
    bootstrapping is available to estimate uncertainty. Several model assessment
    tools are also available. Recent updates include the direct estimation of robust
    standard errors, given a panel structure.
Version: 1.03
Date: 2021-03-05
